Fighting
========

<blockquote cite='https://www.wikidata.org/wiki/Q5204166'>
  <p>Competence in unarmed combat.</p>
</blockquote>

__Based On:__ <span vocab='https://schema.org/' typeof='characterAttribute'>Reflexes</span>.

__Description:__ A <q cite=''>Weaponless Fighing Style</q>

### Specializations &lt;Weaponless Fighting Style&gt;

_Martial Arts:_ Martial artists can deal out accurate strikes and block incoming attacks.

_Wrestling:_ Wrestlers specialize in grappling, restraining, and moving opponents.

_Brawling:_ Brawlers use everything from wild punches to shin kicks and even improvised weapons. 
